cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a new loss function for deep neural networks in image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves regularization and optimization techniques, which are common in sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with abnormal inputs, such as adversarial examples, which could be related to sub-categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
